ZH: 地球是我们生活的家园。
EN: Earth is our home.
ZH: 人类必须爱护地球。
EN: Humans must take care of the Earth.
ZH: 地球上有很多美丽的景观。
EN: There are many beautiful landscapes on Earth.
ZH: 地球上有七大洲。
EN: There are seven continents on Earth.
ZH: 地球上有很多不同的动植物。
EN: There are many different animals and plants on Earth.
ZH: 地球是太阳系中的第三颗行星。
EN: Earth is the third planet in the solar system.
ZH: 地球上70%的表面被海洋覆盖。
EN: 70% of Earth's surface is covered by oceans.
ZH: 地球的周长大约是4万公里。
EN: The circumference of Earth is approximately 40,000 kilometers.
ZH: 地球的内部有熔岩和岩石层。
EN: The interior of Earth contains layers of molten lava and rock.
ZH: 地球被一个层层结构的大气包围。
EN: Earth is surrounded by a layered structure of atmosphere.
ZH: 地球的自转周期大约是24小时。
EN: The rotation period of Earth is approximately 24 hours.
ZH: 地球的卫星是月球。
EN: Earth's satellite is the Moon.
ZH: 地球的自转导致了昼夜的变化。
EN: Earth's rotation causes the changes between day and night.
ZH: 地球的公转周期是一年。
EN: Earth's orbit period is one year.
ZH: 地球的自转轴倾角约为23.5度。
EN: Earth's axial tilt is approximately 23.5 degrees.
ZH: 地球上有很多不同的气候区域。
EN: There are many different climate regions on Earth.
ZH: 地球是我们赖以生存的星球。
EN: Earth is the planet we rely on for survival.
ZH: 地球是唯一已知存在生命的行星。
EN: Earth is the only known planet with life.
ZH: 地球上的生物种类之多令人叹为观止。
EN: The diversity of species on Earth is astounding.
